Understood — dropping NocoBase entirely. Next.js (App Router) as the full-stack application layer, npm as package manager, PostgreSQL as the source of truth, Drizzle as the ORM against the schema you already have.

## SECTION 1: ARCHITECTURE

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Cloudflare → NGINX (TLS, rate limit, mTLS on /ra/*)         │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Next.js 15 (App Router) — Node runtime, standalone output   │
│  ├─ /(admin)   staff console      → RSC + Server Actions     │
│  ├─ /(portal)  client portal      → RSC + Server Actions     │
│  ├─ /api/v1/*  REST (Hono)        → external + n8n           │
│  └─ /api/webhooks/* (Stripe, GlobalSign, DocuSign)           │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  packages/db (Drizzle) │ packages/auth │ packages/policy      │
│  packages/storage      │ packages/jobs │ packages/crypto      │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  PG 16 (RLS) │ Redis (sessions/queue) │ MinIO │ pgvector      │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Worker (BullMQ, separate container) │ pg_cron (in-DB)        │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**The load-bearing decision:** every request runs as a *scoped* PG connection with `app.actor_id` / `app.tenant_id` set. RLS is not a backstop — it's the primary authorization boundary. Application code cannot bypass it because the app role has no `BYPASSRLS`.

```
intune/
├─ apps/
│  ├─ web/                  # Next.js
│  └─ worker/               # BullMQ processor
├─ packages/
│  ├─ db/                   # Drizzle schema, client, RLS scoping
│  ├─ auth/                 # sessions, MFA, Entra OIDC
│  ├─ policy/               # CASL abilities + SoD engine
│  ├─ crypto/               # pgcrypto envelope, hashing, signing
│  ├─ storage/              # MinIO presign, AV scan
│  ├─ jobs/                 # queue defs + processors
│  ├─ contracts/            # zod schemas shared client/server
│  └─ observability/        # pino, OTel
├─ sql/                     # 00–99 migrations from prior build
├─ docker-compose.yml
└─ package.json
```

